# Firebase Configuration
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your-firebase-api-key-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env in the client directory
# 2. Go to Firebase Console (https://console.firebase.google.com/)
# 3. Create or select your project
# 4. Go to Project Settings > General > Web apps
# 5. Copy your Firebase API key and paste it above
# 6. Make sure the key starts with "VITE_" for Vite to recognize it

# Note: Other Firebase config values (authDomain, projectId, etc.) 
# can be hardcoded in firebase.js as they are not sensitive
